<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes, the book can be read on its own. At least as far as the preceding books are concerned, the only overlap is in the universe and themes Banks creat<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes, the book can be read on its own. At least as far as the preceding books are concerned, the only overlap is in the universe and themes Banks created. The characters are unique and the narrative self contained.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
